ref: 14404 *kūpatya -- : Sh.gur. kuiōčh m. ʻ villager ʼ (→ Mai.ky. kuōč ʻ villager ʼ, Bur. kuyōč ʻ subjects of a ruler ʼ): prob. der. kúi (< kūˊpa -- 1 or kuṭī -- ) with suffix -- ōč(h) (as in Sh. koh. koṭōčṷ m. ʻ villager ʼ ~ kōṭ ʻ village ʼ < kōṭṭa -- 1) of doubtful origin (< ápatya -- ? Semant. cf. H. gãwār ʻ villager ʼ < grāmadāra -- ).
